  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FRIGORE</strong> is a simple classic First-person survival horror game , made by one person. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Frigore is a simple classic survival shooter game. The game is still in work and more updates are on the way ! Survive as long as you can in a cold weather environment that will fight against you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Currently updated to version 3.0 which revamped the whole game after a long time.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Cold atmosphere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Constant loot spawns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Global zombie spawn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Creepy atmosphere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p>",
